<p>While the Agency Authorization Playbook is written to inform federal agencies approaching the FedRAMP Authorization process, the information is helpful to all FedRAMP stakeholders.</p>

<p><strong>Updates included information on the following:</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li>Leveraging the FedRAMP Marketplace</li>
  <li>Understanding the FedRAMP reuse process</li>
  <li>The FedRAMP Agency Liaison program</li>
